# 🚀 Usage Examples

## 📌 1. Filter by type

```
GET /api/transactions/filter?type=expense
```

## 📌 2. Filter by category

```
GET /api/transactions/filter?category=Food
```

## 📌 3. Filter by amount range

```
GET /api/transactions/filter?minAmount=500&maxAmount=5000
```

## 📌 4. Filter by date range

```
GET /api/transactions/filter?startDate=2025-01-01&endDate=2025-02-01
```

## 📌 5. Search by notes

```
GET /api/transactions/filter?search=dinner
```

## 📌 6. Pagination

```
GET /api/transactions/filter?page=2&limit=10
```

## 📌 Combine everything

```
GET /api/transactions/filter?type=expense&category=Food&minAmount=100&maxAmount=2000&search=lunch
```

